{"tid":1302884,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【反修例】涂謹申：大埔清牆荒謬","createTime":"2019-07-10T05:59:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-10T06:15:52.000Z","uid":212626,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"0113375a61a14843612ff1ccd377b843016c1df8","tid":1302884,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T05:59:56.000Z","msg":"反修例爭議持續，抗爭行動「遍地開花」，其中大埔墟火車站外的連儂牆，今日（10日）凌晨被發現有逾百警員開展行動，歷時約10分鐘，被市民發現撕走部分涉及警員人身攻擊及「起底」的字條。民主黨涂謹申稱，<span style=\"color: red;\">從媒體看到的畫面感到荒謬，質疑警方出動人員的數目不合比例，他也質疑警方做法是否有法律理據。</span><br />\n<br />\n涂又稱，行會大部分成員現時已無公信力，建議政府立即大幅度改組，另覓人選，包括撤換湯家驊、葉劉淑儀等成員，免其言論再激發民憤；建議可加入運輸及房屋局前局長張炳良、終審法院前首席法官李國能等人，聆聽各界聲音。<br />\n<br />\n他又認為，特首林鄭月娥應盡快辭職，否則應報請中央，按問責制撤換律政司司長鄭若驊和保安局局長李家超。<br />\n<a href=\"https://topick.hket.com/article/2396640/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2396640%2F&d=QYAfZ%2BMwCyPDsUhWB4j8CkuhYyo0AmqkWOXXUYRqYBI%3D&h=7f8a4c5a\" target=\"_blank\">https://topick.hket.com/article/2396640/</a>"},{"pid":"4f7eca1d156f17ecd494d2eecf9697a5797dbc18","tid":1302884,"uid":212626,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T06:01:30.000Z","msg":"建議政府立即大幅度改組，另覓人選，包括撤換<span style=\"color: red;\">湯家驊</span>、<span style=\"color: red;\">葉劉淑儀</span>等成員，<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">免其言論再激發民憤</span></span>；<br />\n雪廠驊同葡萄淑儀表示強烈不滿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f50e52bc294b3ecff971faa4b96c39db07df408d","tid":1302884,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T06:05:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f131777b092eb46dc668e58e872ec962d8a2b533","tid":1302884,"uid":166117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T06:09:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2F50VqF.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2F50VqF.png&h=67339252&s={SI